{"tid":2395023,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"政府： 15個花市將改為取票入場 每票最多兩人 希望市民「快買快賣」 盡快離場","createTime":"2021-02-04T15:08:32.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-05T20:10:55.000Z","uid":22556,"like":5,"dislike":28,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"f90c56fe08bdf3f5a9f7beff5cc546ae21fbd470","tid":2395023,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T15:08:32.000Z","msg":"年宵花市採取燈號人流管制　市民憑票入場每票兩人<br />\n<br />\n全港15個地點本星期六至年三十晚復辦年宵花市，政府說，場地屆時會採取紅、黃、綠燈人流管制。食環署表示，15個場地將嚴格執行防疫抗疫措施，現場設有紅外線傳感器以計算場內人數，綠燈代表人流較少，無須取票進場；黃色代表人流增多，市民須取票輪候進場；紅色代表場內及輪候人數眾多，輪候時間會比較長。市民可於銷售點現場取票，或下載免費流動應用程式遙距取票，所取票號只在當天有效，由召集進場起計的60分鐘內可憑票進場，每票不多於兩人。署方又提醒，前往花市的市民應「快買快賣」，在購買年花後離開銷售點，減少人群聚集。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1574165-20210204.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1574165-20210204.htm&d=GtJgxCFvwMhqeg%2B2Fxb9Eb2U0TaxigNo3Nw2L1ZdNcs%3D&h=69f79df2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1574165-20210204.htm&h=0ded8949\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1574165-20210204.htm</a>"},{"pid":"49c94e85f298cfc668bc7fab5274988ee380e3ac","tid":2395023,"uid":60924,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T15:10:55.000Z","msg":"一二三，紅綠燈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5efa66a6db0dfe9a071039d9aed389198c15162","tid":2395023,"uid":2959,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T15:13:43.000Z","msg":"你鍾意啦 反正都唔會去<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72f342c13ed3f97c33d5ffa86c1d482850e7d4bd","tid":2395023,"uid":107681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T15:14:52.000Z","msg":"買完好過主喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lo